sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant LS as Live Service
    participant ETS as Event Tracking Service
    participant V as Viewer Count Service
    participant R as Redis
    participant K as Kafka

    Note over LS,K: 1. Stream Started
    LS->>K: publish StreamStarted {streamId, creatorId}
    K->>V: consume StreamStarted
    V->>R: SET active_stream:{streamId} "alive"
    R-->>V: OK

    Note over U,K: 2. Join Stream
    U->>ETS: user joins live
    ETS->>K: publish ViewerJoined {streamId, userId}
    K->>V: consume ViewerJoined
    V->>R: EXISTS active_stream:{streamId}
    R-->>V: 1 (active)
    V->>R: SADD stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
    alt new viewer
        V->>R: INCR viewer_count
        V->>R: SETEX stream:{streamId}:viewer:{userId} 60
    else duplicate
        V->>R: SETEX stream:{streamId}:viewer:{userId} 60
    end

    Note over U,K: 3. Heartbeat
    loop every 30s
        U->>ETS: user still watching
        ETS->>K: publish ViewerHeartbeat {streamId, userId}
        K->>V: consume ViewerHeartbeat
        V->>R: SETEX stream:{streamId}:viewer:{userId} 60
    end

    Note over U,K: 4. Leave Stream
    U->>ETS: user leaves live
    ETS->>K: publish ViewerLeft {streamId, userId}
    K->>V: consume ViewerLeft
    V->>R: SREM stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
    alt removed
        V->>R: DECR viewer_count
        V->>R: DEL stream:{streamId}:viewer:{userId}
    else not found
        Note over V: Ignore
    end

    Note over V,R: 5. Ghost User
    R->>V: EXPIRED stream:{streamId}:viewer:{userId}
    V->>R: SISMEMBER stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
    R-->>V: 1 or 0
    alt exists
        V->>R: SREM stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
        V->>R: DECR stream:{streamId}:viewer_count
    else already removed
        Note over V: Ignore
    end

    Note over LS,K: 6. Stream Ended
    LS->>K: publish StreamEnded {streamId}
    K->>V: consume StreamEnded
    V->>R: DEL active_stream:{streamId}
    V->>R: DEL stream:{streamId}:viewer_count
    V->>R: DEL stream:{streamId}:viewers
    R-->>V: OK

    Note over U,R: 7. Get Viewer Count
    U->>V: GET /streams/{streamId}/viewers
    V->>R: GET stream:{streamId}:viewer_count
    R-->>V: N
    V-->>U: 200 OK {viewerCount: N}